clang-analyzer-nullability.NullPassedToN.description:
Description

clang-analyzer-nullability.NullPassedToNonnull
Warns when a null pointer is passed to a pointer which has a _Nonnull type.
The
clang-analyzer-nullability.NullPassedToNonnull
check is an alias, please see
Clang Static Analyzer Available Checkers
for more information.
clang-analyzer-nullability.NullPassedToN.option:
Static analysis (Clang-Tidy) options are configured via .clang-tidy file.

This rule has no specific options.
